23:03.215 --> 23:04.675
<i>You know, if--</i>
<i>if we have it down here,</i>

23:04.675 --> 23:06.176
<i>there's a better chance</i>
<i>his whole family can come,</i>

23:06.176 --> 23:07.386
<i>you know?</i>

23:09.221 --> 23:12.808
- I mean, we can change it,

23:12.808 --> 23:14.393
but then, like,
my friends and family

23:14.393 --> 23:16.312
are gonna have a hard time
making it down there too.

23:16.312 --> 23:18.439
- But Coco didn't know
any of them.

23:22.276 --> 23:24.361
- Oh, my God, wait.
I just realized

23:24.361 --> 23:26.071
this would be
such a nice getaway

23:26.071 --> 23:27.865
for Lynn and the girls,
don't you think?

23:27.865 --> 23:29.283
<i>I guess.</i>

23:29.283 --> 23:31.577
A fun adventure
to take their mind off things.

23:34.914 --> 23:36.332
<i>Are you still there?</i>

23:36.332 --> 23:38.334
- Yeah.

23:38.334 --> 23:41.003
- I already paid the deposit
for the field.

23:41.003 --> 23:42.796
It's non-refundable.

23:43.756 --> 23:45.966
But I could change it
if you want.

23:45.966 --> 23:47.885
I don't want this
to be a thing.

23:48.677 --> 23:50.512
- No, no, it's fine.

23:52.598 --> 23:55.434
I'll call Coco's league and see
who wants to make the drive.

23:55.434 --> 23:58.854
- That would be amazing.
Conrad would've loved that.

24:00.272 --> 24:01.649
- Yeah.

24:01.649 --> 24:03.150
You're such
<i>an amazing friend, Rob.</i>

24:03.150 --> 24:06.695
We're gonna make this event
perfect for him.

24:06.695 --> 24:10.199
You can be my co-captain
to finalize organizing.

24:10.199 --> 24:11.533
- Co-captain?

24:11.533 --> 24:12.910
I'm so excited.
<i>I got to go,</i>

24:12.910 --> 24:15.371
but, uh, let's--let's talk
about it later, okay?

24:15.371 --> 24:17.206
Bye.
Thank you, bye.

24:25.422 --> 24:28.050
- Michelle, everything okay?
- I'm fine.

24:28.968 --> 24:30.844
Can we put the deposit
down now?

24:31.470 --> 24:33.222
Sure.

24:43.649 --> 24:46.360
Gotta do something fun
for your last day.

24:46.360 --> 24:48.070
- Cute.

24:52.992 --> 24:54.743
Hey, wait for me.

24:54.743 --> 24:55.953
- Why?

24:55.953 --> 24:57.246
- Dad said I could come.

24:57.246 --> 24:58.372
- Are you fucking--

24:58.372 --> 25:00.207
- Hi, I'm Sydney.

25:00.207 --> 25:01.458
- Michelle.

25:01.458 --> 25:03.377
- You Coco's girlfriend?

25:04.169 --> 25:05.546
- Mm-mm.

25:05.546 --> 25:07.381
- Where are we going?

25:10.426 --> 25:11.844
You're prettier than the girls
